    "introduction": "《背蓝书包的小女孩》是墨西哥影史上最经典的儿童片，曾在墨西哥国内创下观看人数最高纪录，几乎每个墨西哥小孩都曾看过这部影片，童年时对电影的美好回忆。这部影片在81年又拍了续集，同样获得了成功。One of the most popular and successful family films in Mexican history tells the story of the love shared between two children regardless of their social standing. Pedro Fernandez--who's successful recording career began as a result of this production--stars as a young man who struggles with his feelings for orphaned Maria Rebeca, who's impoverished lifestyle draws ridicule at school.",
